# Models, checkpoints, corpus — sync từ MinIO/HF mirror nội bộ
# NOTE: this ignores ML-weight dirs named `models/` anywhere, but must NOT
# swallow the Python source package `src/pharmagpt_vn/models/` (the LLM-client
# package). The negation below keeps that source tree tracked.
models/
!src/pharmagpt_vn/models/
!src/pharmagpt_vn/models/**
# …but keep bytecode/caches ignored even inside the re-included source package.
src/pharmagpt_vn/models/**/__pycache__/
src/pharmagpt_vn/models/**/*.py[cod]
data/raw/
data/processed/
data/corpus_vn_pharma/
runs/
*.safetensors
*.bin
*.gguf

# wandb
wandb/

.ipynb_checkpoints/
